Dear Narasimha,

> When you do homam, think that god is indeed in the fire.
> Be thankful to fire and to god.


We invoke the devata in agni and try to feel his presence there. At the same
time, we say that agni, as havyavaaha, takes the offerings to the devata.
Isn't there an inherent contradiction?

   ajit





